title: SPELLLING performs Live on KEXP from 25th Street Recording in Oakland, CA

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents SPELLLING performing live at 25th Street Recording in Oakland, California, during Noise Pop 2025. Recorded February 27, 2025.

Songs:
Drain  00:24
Alibi  01:05
Waterfall  08:52
Portrait Of My Heart 12:10

Tia Cabral - Vocals
Wyatt Overson -Guitar
Patrick Shelley - Drums
Giulio Cetto - Bass
Bella King - Keys
Dharma Mooney Haynes - Backup Vocals
Natoya Willock - Backup Vocals

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Guest Audio Engineer: Gabriel Shepard, Karishma Kumar, Collin Purdue
Audio Mixer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht

25th Street Crew:
Gabriel Shepard
Karishma Kumar
Collin Purdue
